Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iFieldEventType FIELDTYPE_FOOTBALL = 1 FIELDTYPE_SOCCER = 2 FIELDTYPE_SPECIAL = 3
if iFieldEventType = FIELDTYPE_SOCCER then aa=105 bb=68 endif if iFieldEventType = FIELDTYPE_FOOTBALL then aa=109 bb=48.8+15 endif
!*** resolution of cylinds
gs_res_2=16
Symbol.Script_VL:
values{2} "iFieldEventType" FIELDTYPE_FOOTBALL, `Футбольное Поле`, FIELDTYPE_SOCCER, `Поле для Соккера`, FIELDTYPE_SPECIAL, `Специальное Поле`
if iFieldEventType <> FIELDTYPE_SPECIAL then lock "aa", "bb" endif
values "aa" range [340',400'] values "bb" range [200',330']
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_detlevel_3d" `Детальный`,`Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3d_m" 0, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3d" then gs_detlevel_3d_m = 0 if gs_detlevel_3d = `Детальный` then gs_detlevel_3d_m = 2 parameters gs_detlevel_3d_m = gs_detlevel_3d_m else gs_detlevel_3d = `Откл.` if gs_detlevel_3d_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_3d = `Детальный` parameters gs_detlevel_3d = gs_detlevel_3d endif
